Hélène Fillières https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/H%C3%A9l%C3%A8ne_Filli%C3%A8res 0 Hélène Fillières (born 1 May 1972) is a French actress, film director and screenwriter. She is the sister of filmmaker Sophie Fillières. Hélène_Fillières ( born 1_May_1972 ) is a_French_actress , film_director_and_screenwriter . She is the_sister of filmmaker_Sophie_Fillières .
